com.interpss.core.aclf.contingency

Interface BusbarOutageContingency

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseContingency, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, MultiOutageContingency, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BusbarOutageContingencyImpl

    public interface BusbarOutageContingency
extends MultiOutageContingency
    A representation of the model object 'Busbar Outage Contingency'. A class for modeling a Busbar outage contingency

    The following features are supported:

    • Busbar Name
    • Outage Bus Id
    • Power Loss
    • Power Loss Dist Buses
    See Also:
    ContingencyPackage.getBusbarOutageContingency()
